.TH IMGMOD-OPTIM 1
.SH NAME
imgmod-optim \- optimize an image directly
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B imgmod optim
[\fB-h\fR] \fIINPUT\fR [\fIOUTPUT\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Optimize an image file with image_optim.

If \fIOUTPUT\fR is omitted, the input is optimized in place. If \fIOUTPUT\fR is
provided, the input is copied there first and the copy is optimized.
